---
import PageLayout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  metadata={{
    title: 'Firmware Changelog — OWON Developers',
    description: 'Firmware version history for OWON IoT devices.',
  }}
>
  <section class="py-12">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex gap-8">
        <nav class="hidden lg:block w-56 shrink-0 sticky top-24 self-start space-y-1">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-muted mb-3 tracking-wider">Developers</p>
          <a
            href="/developers"
            class="block px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm text-muted hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-800 hover:text-default transition-colors"
            >Overview</a
          >
          <a
            href="/developers/api"
            class="block px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm text-muted hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-800 hover:text-default transition-colors"
            >API Reference</a
          >
          <a
            href="/developers/sdks"
            class="block px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm text-muted hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-800 hover:text-default transition-colors"
            >SDKs & Libraries</a
          >
          <a
            href="/developers/examples"
            class="block px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm text-muted hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-800 hover:text-default transition-colors"
            >Code Examples</a
          >
          <a
            href="/developers/changelog"
            class="block px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium bg-primary/10 text-primary">Firmware Changelog</a
          >
        </nav>
        <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
          <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2 text-default dark:text-slate-100">Firmware Changelog</h1>
          <p class="text-muted dark:text-slate-400 mb-8">
            Firmware release history for OWON IoT devices. All updates are delivered OTA.
          </p>

          <!-- Filter tabs -->
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-10">
            <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-primary text-white">All Devices</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-gray-100 dark:bg-slate-700 text-muted">Smart Meters</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-gray-100 dark:bg-slate-700 text-muted">Thermostats</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-gray-100 dark:bg-slate-700 text-muted">Hotel Control</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-gray-100 dark:bg-slate-700 text-muted">Senior Care</span>
          </div>

          <!-- Changelog entries -->
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <!-- v2.2.0 -->
            <div class="relative pl-8 border-l-2 border-primary/30 pb-6">
              <div class="absolute left-[-9px] top-0 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-primary border-2 border-white dark:border-slate-900"></div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2 flex-wrap">
                <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-bold bg-green-500 text-white">v2.2.0</span>
                <time class="text-xs text-muted">June 28, 2026</time>
                <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/30 text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-300">Smart Meters</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-default dark:text-slate-200 mb-2">MQTT 5.0 Support + Improved Calibration</h3>
              <ul class="text-sm text-muted dark:text-slate-400 space-y-1 list-disc pl-4">
                <li>Added MQTT 5.0 protocol support alongside 3.1.1 (auto-negotiate)</li>
                <li>Improved voltage measurement accuracy: ±0.5% → ±0.2%</li>
                <li>Added session persistence across broker restarts</li>
                <li>Fixed rare memory leak during extended TLS reconnection</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- v2.1.4 -->
            <div class="relative pl-8 border-l-2 border-primary/30 pb-6">
              <div class="absolute left-[-9px] top-0 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-primary border-2 border-white dark:border-slate-900"></div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2 flex-wrap">
                <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-bold bg-green-500 text-white">v2.1.4</span>
                <time class="text-xs text-muted">May 15, 2026</time>
                <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/30 text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-300">Smart Meters</span>
                <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-900/30 text-purple-700 dark:text-purple-300">Hotel Control</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-default dark:text-slate-200 mb-2">OTA Delta Updates + Hotel Panel Fix</h3>
              <ul class="text-sm text-muted dark:text-slate-400 space-y-1 list-disc pl-4">
                <li>Introduced delta OTA updates — only download changed firmware blocks (60-80% smaller)</li>
                <li>Fixed hotel room panel display freeze after 7+ days of continuous uptime</li>
                <li>Reduced OTA update time from ~4 min to ~90 sec for incremental updates</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- v2.1.1 -->
            <div class="relative pl-8 border-l-2 border-primary/30 pb-6">
              <div class="absolute left-[-9px] top-0 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-primary border-2 border-white dark:border-slate-900"></div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2 flex-wrap">
                <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-bold bg-green-500 text-white">v2.1.1</span>
                <time class="text-xs text-muted">April 3, 2026</time>
                <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs bg-orange-100 dark:bg-orange-900/30 text-orange-700 dark:text-orange-300">Thermostats</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-default dark:text-slate-200 mb-2">Thermostat Scheduling + Energy Report Export</h3>
              <ul class="text-sm text-muted dark:text-slate-400 space-y-1 list-disc pl-4">
                <li>Added weekly scheduling — set temperature targets per time slot, per day</li>
                <li>Energy usage CSV export via REST API (GET /devices/:id/energy-report)</li>
                <li>Improved PID auto-tuning for radiator valve thermostats</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- v2.0.0 -->
            <div class="relative pl-8 pb-6">
              <div class="absolute left-[-9px] top-0 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-gray-300 dark:bg-slate-600 border-2 border-white dark:border-slate-900"></div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2 flex-wrap">
                <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-bold bg-gray-500 text-white">v2.0.0</span>
                <time class="text-xs text-muted">February 10, 2026</time>
                <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/30 text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-300">Smart Meters</span>
                <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs bg-orange-100 dark:bg-orange-900/30 text-orange-700 dark:text-orange-300">Thermostats</span>
                <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-900/30 text-purple-700 dark:text-purple-300">Hotel Control</span>
                <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/30 text-green-700 dark:text-green-300">Senior Care</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-default dark:text-slate-200 mb-2">Unified Firmware Platform v2</h3>
              <ul class="text-sm text-muted dark:text-slate-400 space-y-1 list-disc pl-4">
                <li>Merged all device firmwares onto a single platform kernel</li>
                <li>Unified OTA pipeline — one endpoint for all OWON devices</li>
                <li>TLS 1.3 only (dropped TLS 1.2 for enhanced security)</li>
                <li>New bootloader with fallback partition (A/B update scheme)</li>
                <li><strong>⚠ Breaking:</strong> Requires bootloader update before flashing v2.0+</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
